## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="379a0-102"><xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions>类提供了<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.Ttl%2A>和<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.DontFragment%2A>属性来控制 Internet 控制消息协议 (ICMP) 回显请求数据包的传输方式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="379a0-102">The <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions> class provides the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.Ttl%2A> and <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.DontFragment%2A> properties to control how Internet Control Message Protocol (ICMP) echo request packets are transmitted.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="379a0-103"><xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.Ttl%2A>属性指定发送的数据包的生存时间<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="379a0-103">The <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.Ttl%2A> property specifies the Time to Live for packets sent by the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="379a0-104">此值指示可以转发的路由节点数<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping>之前它将被丢弃的数据包。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="379a0-104">This value indicates the number of routing nodes that can forward a <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping> packet before it is discarded.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="379a0-105">设置此选项很有用，如果你想要测试的转发数，也称为跃点，则还需要将数据包从源计算机发送到目标计算机。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="379a0-105">Setting this option is useful if you want to test the number of forwards, also known as hops, are required to send a packet from a source computer to a destination computer.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="379a0-106"><xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.DontFragment%2A>属性控制是否将数据发送到远程主机可以划分为多个数据包。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="379a0-106">The <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.DontFragment%2A> property controls whether data sent to a remote host can be divided into multiple packets.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="379a0-107">此选项非常有用，如果你想要测试的最大传输单位 (MTU) 的路由器和网关用来传输该数据包。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="379a0-107">This option is useful if you want to test the maximum transmission unit (MTU) of the routers and gateways used to transmit the packet.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="379a0-108">实例<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions>类传递给<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping.Send%2A>并<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping.SendAsync%2A>方法，和<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingReply>类返回的实例<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions>通过<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingReply.Options%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="379a0-108">Instances of the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions> class are passed to the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping.Send%2A> and <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping.SendAsync%2A> methods, and the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingReply> class returns instances of <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions> via the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingReply.Options%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="379a0-109">有关实例的初始属性值的列表<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions>，请参阅<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.%23ctor%2A>构造函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="379a0-109">For a list of initial property values for an instance of <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions>, see the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.%23ctor%2A> constructor.</span></span>  
  
   
  
